OL,7,FA controversial large advertising
OL,8,Fscreen above the concourse at Euston
OL,9,Frailway station will be used to
OL,10,Fdisplay train information, Network
OL,11,FRail said.
OL,13,FThe screen stopped being used to show
OL,14,Fadverts in October when then-transport
OL,15,Fsecretary Louise Haigh ordered Network
OL,16,FRail to improve how it manages the
OL,17,Fstation.
