OL,7,F"We've been clear the station simply
OL,8,Fhasn't been good enough for customers,
OL,9,Fand that's why we recently tasked
OL,10,FNetwork Rail with making immediate
OL,11,Fimprovements to address crowding and
OL,12,Fgive passengers the experience they
OL,13,Fdeserve."
OL,15,FGary Walsh, Network Rail's West Coast
OL,16,FSouth route director, said: "After
OL,17,Flistening to our passengers, we're
OL,18,Fpleased to launch a trial to display
OL,19,Ftravel information on Euston station's
OL,20,Flarge screen this week.
