OL,7,F"Our five-point plan is all about
OL,8,Fmaking quick and effective
OL,9,Fimprovements to make journeys smoother
OL,10,Ffor everyone and we're really pleased
OL,11,Fto be able to deliver this in time for
OL,12,Fthe busy festive travel period."
OL,14,FNetwork Rail added it has received a
OL,15,F"positive" response to an initiative
OL,16,Fenabling passengers to board some
OL,17,Fservices earlier.
