OL,7,FOn September 26 last year, regulator
OL,8,Fthe Office of Rail and Road (ORR)
OL,9,Fissued an improvement notice to
OL,10,FNetwork Rail in relation to Euston,
OL,11,Faccusing the company of failing to
OL,12,Fprevent safety risks from
OL,13,F"unacceptable" overcrowding.
OL,15,FThe ORR found Network Rail complied
OL,16,Fwith the notice on December 15 2023,
OL,17,Fbut concerns about the station
OL,18,Fcontinued.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]
