OL,4,Cstation advertisement screen after
OL,5,Ccontroversy
OL,7,FWatchdog London TravelWatch said in
OL,8,Fearly October that "last-minute
OL,9,Fannouncements" caused passengers to
OL,10,F"rush to platforms", and staff "appear
OL,11,Foverwhelmed by the sheer numbers of
OL,12,Fpeople".
OL,14,FTesting of the screen will take place
OL,15,Ftomorrow (11 December) with plans to
OL,16,Ffully activate the screen from next
OL,17,Fweek.
