OL,7,FDuring the testing phase of the
OL,8,Fscreen, passengers are being advised
OL,9,Fto continue to refer to the screens in
OL,10,Fthe middle of the concourse for
OL,11,Faccurate travel information.
OL,13,FMessaging about the testing will also
OL,14,Fbe displayed in the station to keep
OL,15,Fpassengers fully informed.
