OL,7,FThe trial is part of Network Rail's
OL,8,Ffive-point plan of inproving passenger
OL,9,Fexperiences at the station, including
OL,10,Fthe earlier boarding of Avanti West
OL,11,FCoast and London Northwestern Railway
OL,12,Ftrains - which has allowed passengers
OL,13,Fto board at a more relaxed pace and
OL,14,Fcreated a calmer station environment.
OL,16,FPassengers travelling to and from
OL,17,FLondon Euston over the festive period
OL,18,Fhave been advised the station will be
OL,19,Fextremely busy this year due to
OL,20,Fengineering work affecting other major
OL,21,Froutes into London.
